{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Pirates &amp; Pirater</i> is a\u00a0<strong>First-Person Action-Adventure</strong> where pirates have replaced their metal arsenal with fruit, meat &amp; vegetables! <strong>Cook</strong> up your armory, <strong>eat</strong> your weaponry &amp; <strong>fight as</strong>\u00a0a true culinary pirate!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727960/extras/Pock_Hold_Description_Header_01.png?t=1727099749\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727960/extras/Gameplay_Pirates_GIFs_01.gif?t=1727099749\" /><strong>Utilize</strong> your menu of weapons and an array of abilities to combat your way through the pirate hierarchy! Take up the fight by altering your tasty recipes and cooking however many tools you need to change the five-star course of history</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Discover </strong>new ingredients to implement in your armory, <strong>unlock </strong>new recipes to expand your arsenal &amp; <strong>battle</strong> the pantheon of pirate lords! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Liberate </strong>your way through the diverse levels and areas inhabited by quirky characters and enemies as you clear out the evil that has taken hold in <i>Gustav\u2019s Archipelago</i>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727960/extras/Soupmancer_Description_Header_01.png?t=1727099749\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727960/extras/Environment_GIF_Pirates_Pirater_01.gif?t=1727099749\" /><strong>Explore </strong>a succulent world ruled by a clan of <strong>soup-worshiping pirates</strong> as you embark on a cu